<div><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:=
10pt">Title&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs=
p;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; :
<strong>Plasmonic Biosensors for Clinical Diagnosis</strong></span><br styl=
e=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt">
<br style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt">
<span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt"=
>Date &amp; Time &nbsp; : </span>
<strong style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10p=
t"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif">20th July, 2=
015 (Wednesday) at 04:00PM</span></strong><br style=3D"font-family:&quot;Se=
goe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt">
<br style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt">
<span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt"=
>Venue&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nb=
sp;&nbsp; :
</span><strong style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-s=
ize:10pt"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif">Newto=
n Hall (</span></strong><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,san=
s-serif; font-size:10pt">near&nbsp;Aerospace Building</span><strong style=
=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt"><span styl=
e=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif">)</span></strong><br styl=
e=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt">
<br style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt">
<strong style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10p=
t"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif">Abstract:
</span></strong><br style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; f=
ont-size:10pt">
<br style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt">
<span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt"=
>Disease biomarkers, such as prostrate specific antigen (PSA) and cardiac t=
roponin I (cTnI) for early diagnosis of prostrate cancer and myocardial inf=
arction (heart attack) respectively, require
 detection sensitivities from femto (10-15) down to atto (10-18) -molar con=
centrations. Optical fibers are promising substrates exploited for both lab=
el-free and labelled biosensing applications due to their inherent advantag=
es including high absorbance sensitivity
 and compactness. Our previous studies demonstrated a proof-of-concept of c=
ost effective and high sensitive evanescence wave absorbance (EWA) based fi=
ber optic biosensor by exploiting plasmonic nanoparticles (AuNP) as labels =
on a U-bent optical probe. A sequential
 sandwich assay was demonstrated for detection of human immunoglobulin (HIg=
G) as a model, using 13nm immunogold (Goat anti-human IgG conjugated AuNP) =
particles. This assay was performed in 1 hour and 20 min and a sensitivity =
of 0.3 ng/ml (2 pM) was obtained.
</span><br style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:=
10pt">
<br style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt">
<span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt"=
>In this context, our current study presents the latest results with 2 orde=
r further enhancement in sensitivity and faster assay time (20 min) by adop=
ting 40 nm immunogold particles. The new strategy
 (spontaneous assay) gives rise to femtomolar (6.67fM or 1pg/ml) detection =
limit within an assay time of 20 mins. Subsequent immunogold-silver stainin=
g (IGSS) process utilizing catalytic property of gold nanoparticles leads t=
o a 10&#8203;00-fold enhancement in detection
 limit (LOD) within 5 min. The ability to <strong>detect 1&nbsp;fg/mL&nbsp;=
or&nbsp;</strong><strong>100 molecules
</strong>in a sample&nbsp;demonstrates a huge potential for development of =
sensitive and rapid detection based point-of-care diagnosis with simple han=
d-held instrumentation and reagent accessories.</span><br style=3D"font-fam=
ily:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt">
<br style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt">
<span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt"=
>All are Welcome</span><br style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-s=
erif; font-size:10pt">
<br style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt">
<span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:10pt"=
